- `/v1/models` → `GET https://<middleman>/internal/models`
- `/v1/price` → `GET https://<middleman>/internal/quote?model=...`
- `/v1/agent/ping` → `GET https://<middleman>/internal/ping`
- `/v1/execute` (once live) → `POST https://<middleman>/internal/execute`

